-- Japan: Mitsubishi Heavy, IHI to participate on F-35
-- 
-- Mon Dec 19, 2011 10:50pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/20/us-lockheed-japan-f35-participation-idUSTRE7BJ0CE20111220

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Japan's defense ministry said on Tuesday that Mitsubishi Heavy Industries Ltd would participate in the production of Lockheed Martin's F-35 jet, which Japan has chosen as its next mainstay fighter. 
 The ministry also said that IHI Corp would also participate. (Reporting by  Kiyoshi Takenaka ; Editing by  Chris Gallagher )